    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <opener><dateline><placeName ref="pl0001">Downing</placeName> May 23<hi rend="superscript">rd</hi> 1773.</dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Sir</salute></opener>
                <p>Excuse my troubling you on the strength of y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> kind
                    offer of services: I am most desirous of some accounts of the pictures at
                    <placeName ref="pl0150">Tarnaway castle</placeName>: I applied to <persName ref="pe0583">Lord Kinnoul</persName> &amp; his Lordship refers them to you. if you are
                    so good as to get them answered, be pleased to transmit y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> favor by means of my good friend <persName ref="pe0020">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Oliphant</persName> of <placeName ref="pl0289">Rossie</placeName>: perhaps you may have some further trouble from
                    <persName ref="pe0168">M<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Marshall</persName> about
                    the old fosses on y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> demean. I hope <persName ref="pe1998">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi> Mackenzie</persName> is in perfect
                    health, &amp; beg my best complim<hi rend="superscript">ts</hi>.</p>
                <closer><salute>I am Dear Sir with much esteem <lb/>Y<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>
                        obliged &amp; <lb/>most obed<hi rend="superscript">t</hi> Serv<hi rend="superscript">t</hi></salute>
                    <signed><persName ref="pe0232">Tho. Pennant</persName></signed></closer>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p><address>
                        <addrLine>To</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>John Mackenzie Esq<hi rend="superscript">r</hi>:</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>of Delvin</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>near Perth</addrLine>
                        <addrLine>North <hi rend="underline">Britain</hi></addrLine>
                    </address></p>
                <p>Free <persName ref="pe0313">Rich. Bull</persName></p>
                <p><stamp type="frank">FREE</stamp></p>
                <p><stamp type="handstamp">H</stamp></p>
                <p><stamp type="postmark">26/MA</stamp></p>
                <p><stamp type="postmark">27/MA</stamp></p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
